question: What is the current population of Odense, Denmark as of 2024?
asked_question_translated: Hvor mange indbyggere er der i Odense, Danmark, i 2024?
answer: Pr. 2024 forventes Odense, Danmark, at have omkring 180.000-190.000 indbyggere.
answer_translated_eng: By 2024, Odense, Denmark is expected to have around 180,000-190,000 inhabitants.
